data.value: CafeStock is an inventory management system specifically designed for the cafeteria of Mapua Malayan Colleges Mindanao. Built using Windows Forms in C++/CLI, it features a secure login system for administrators, a user-friendly dashboard, tools for tracking and updating inventory, historical data viewing, and a logout function. This system aims to streamline cafeteria operations, ensuring efficient stock management and improved service delivery for the college community.
